ATTRIBUTION AND ACKNOWLEDGMENTS:

This project incorporates substantial code and architecture from:

1. trunk-recorder project (GNU General Public License v3)
   - Core P25 processing algorithms
   - IMBE vocoder integration methods
   - Frame handling and parsing logic
   - JSON metadata generation techniques
   This project builds directly on trunk-recorder's excellent implementation.

2. OP25 project (GNU General Public License v3)
   - P25 protocol implementation
   - IMBE frame parsing
   - Digital signal processing components

3. IMBE Vocoder implementation by Pavel Yazev (GPL compatible)
   - Fixed-point IMBE encoder/decoder

